{"tid":1345520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗同中環缺一不可","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:14:16.000Z","uid":38793,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8171d1c82c174815feef6b097015a5bf44c2b08c","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"點解依家元朗事件洗晒版？<br />\n因為黑社會冇差別打人 我哋係完全企喺道德嘅至高點<br />\n如果話警察開槍都有藍黃兩方陣營意見嘅話<br />\n咁我諗元朗呢單係黑社會同政府完全錯晒<br />\n所以既然起元朗事件中我哋係零錯誤同無懈可擊<br />\n而家就先將鄉黑打人大肆宣傳<br />\n等民意完全傾向一邊後 再抨擊政府<br />\n隨後將中環事件警察開槍射人與之配合<br />\n兩者互相運用 發揮最大效果"},{"pid":"05e57e8ab4ae8c2a5475652f952cdf037e22cfae","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:16:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c409289886c3eb9963605d1675ed60b458317128","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"54338be3f1d958188ae4986fc72a46bff7e61387","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:16:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"aae26dc6b480c3a1db7a7f6d9a71df2dbcb05728","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6593ec52cc6a5f1fa4374adaeb90087c6153d2da","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2ab7185ca15dbcf8c418915d3a5d8c9711901058","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e3384568a132d2805f8f7e905e0532eb3d5f8226","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8376679208d758b9c35e541131ad858d3a0690bf","tid":1345520,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"546b80997a9847ae4c13170fe9ce5ba62c7